name: 'All Yours, Babooshka'
description:
'All Yours, Babooshka' 

A range of contemporary Illustrated Greeting cards depicting traditional Russian Matryoshka dolls.

'Natalia' - Red
'Frieda' - Blue
'Theodora' - Turquoise

Each pack consists of 6 cards with accompanying white envelopes (2 of each design) and are printed onto 100% recycled 352gsm Mohawk stock.

*(Folded cards measure 14.8 by 10.5cm - A6)
